Consider this less a definitive decree and more a [how-to guide](/Wikipedia:Project_namespace). It's a collection of concepts and processes, cobbled together by a community that occasionally achieves something resembling [consensus](/Wikipedia:Consensus). Do not mistake it for one of [Wikipedia's policies or guidelines](/Wikipedia:Policies_and_guidelines); those are the ones written in blood, or at least, in the tears of countless editors. This? This is merely a suggestion, prone to the shifting sands of collective whims, much like everything else that truly matters.

